{"tid":1738174,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"轉載：煲大紅四代也挺身而出與香港人攜手反共","createTime":"2019-11-19T07:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T10:27:08.000Z","uid":34751,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92249e32574682cb8ff13120a56e0316e96f836d","tid":1738174,"uid":34751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"學識打輿論戰。怒罵曾鈺成營救中共元老曾孫女，這是「公價」貨色；煲大紅四代也挺身而出與香港人攜手反共，這才叫反將一軍。<br />\n<br />\n然後，習近平就會迫朱媛出面否認，甚至拍片割席，哭訴自己被迫困在理大，朱家難道會忍受得住如此辱沒嗎？曾uncle亂喊世姪女芳名，也難辭其咎。<br />\n<br />\n中共權貴大把子女做香港人，他們貪腐得來的資產（包括香港炒樓所得）將來是由他們繼承的，請好好思考這一點。<br />\n<br />\n作者"},{"pid":"1d0f7877ad1704a2236d7a35714341d6f8f0e40c","tid":1738174,"uid":160075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b51742e790c2455f28d5598ccb966bc69288f5f","tid":1738174,"uid":33473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n如果佢真係手足的話<br />\n希望佢體諒下"},{"pid":"8f9b8a60ca060ca86824aa989992df706180ac77","tid":1738174,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:24:09.000Z","msg":"我都唔知佢係咪真<br />\n老鼠做野點會咁唔小心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b9ee0e365906ef469c81a14d253445a06d2ca7","tid":1738174,"uid":81449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21c0b583017a2910ba1e161138dee967031c3b8d","tid":1738174,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T07:29:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1a1a01bc590c018e3038f5820e815c4d57b969c2","tid":1738174,"uid":34751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:26:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a3fdbaac9668a0caafdc34e7a6bc267c23f1adf","tid":1738174,"uid":34751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT